# Department for Transport

Department overview
Formed 29&#160;May 2002;&#32;23 years ago&#160;(2002-05-29)
Jurisdiction [Government of the United Kingdom](/Government_of_the_United_Kingdom)
Headquarters [Great Minster House](/Great_Minster_House), [Horseferry Road](/Horseferry_Road), [London](/London)
